---
title: Spicy Chicken Sandos With Herby Crema plus a Harissa-Spiced Bulgur Salad
description: These spicy chicken sandos are packed to bursting with flavor! You’ll season the chicken with fiery, flavorful harissa powder, sear, and load into toasty brioche buns along with cooling herbed crema, while a nutty bulgur salad on the side gets the same spicy kick along with fresh tomato, cucumber, and scallion.
